com.intland.codebeamer.manager

Class SubscriptionManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intland.codebeamer.manager.SubscriptionManager

  • public class SubscriptionManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Business Layer subscription management.
    1. it does not resolve subscription to parent objects. For example, if you query for the subscription of a tracker item, tracker subscriptions are ignored.

    This hides the details of the different legacy subscription mechanisms that are existing. In the future, this is meant to unify the subscription model for any entity.
